    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_1836_08_30_page01.jpg"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE"/><choice><orig>Edgeworthtown</orig><reg>Edgeworthstown</reg></choice>
                        <date when="1836-08-30">Aug<hi rend="superscript">t.</hi> <unclear>30<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi></unclear> 1836</date></dateline>
                    <salute>
                        Dear Sir
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    Have you written yet to<lb/>
                    <persName ref="./Personography.xml#CarmA1">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Carmichael?</persName><lb/>
                    If you have not I wish you<lb/>
                    would not delay longer to<lb/>
                    do so - for it is most cruel<lb/>
                    to keep her in suspense.<lb/>
                    You promised <persName ref="./Personography.xml#LockJ1">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>.</persName> and<lb/>
                    <persName ref="./Personography.xml#LockS1">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Lockhart</persName> that you would<lb/>
                    write directly -<lb/>
                    If you have written give<lb/>
                    me the satisfaction of a line<lb/>
                    to tell me so - &amp; direct under<lb/>
                    cover to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#DrumT1"><choice><orig>T<hi rend="superscript">s</hi></orig><reg>Thomas</reg></choice> Drummond</persName> Esq<lb/>
                    <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Dublin-Castle_IE">Dublin Castle</placeName> -<lb/>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    Yours truly<lb/>
                    <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName><lb/>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <persName ref="./Personography.xml#CarmA1">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. <choice><orig>Carmichaels</orig><reg>Carmichael's</reg></choice></persName> address is<lb/>
                        S<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. <choice><orig>Helens</orig><reg>Helen's</reg></choice> <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#JE">Jersey</placeName><lb/>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
             </div>
        </body>
        <back> </back>
    </text>
